{"tid":947084,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【市區樓劈價】翔龍灣跌穿600萬 今年新低","createTime":"2018-12-19T04:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T05:23:37.000Z","uid":87069,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d77867b9591d575fab3810644b771afb95b23ca7","tid":947084,"uid":87069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:07:08.000Z","msg":"樓市淡靜，新盤吸去大批購買力，二手業主劈價賣樓。土瓜灣指標屋苑翔龍灣連環三宗劈價，其中一宗更跌穿600萬元，為屋苑今年首度重現「五字頭」成交。<br />\n<br />\n聯通物業黎俊漢表示，翔龍灣剛錄得三宗低價成交，其中2座中層A室，實用面積360方呎，原叫價650萬元，剛減至598萬元沽出，呎價16,611元。同座其樓下兩層A室，面積相同，今年8月以745萬元售出，呎價20,694元，是次成交四個月後賣平147萬元或19.7%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181218/59043817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59043817&d=pvhBAVBnmSzUoSw0xFwVYwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6a362a42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181218%2F59043817&h=cfde4eae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181218/59043817</a><br />\n<br />\n樓下個所謂大商場近年俾大陸團入侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，酒樓唔開放俾街坊飲茶，剩俾大陸人食，跟住又泊哂大巴<br />\n<br />\n恆基sell完你大商場concept，采你都老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd90b4286f11040c11251f878d0ad23441e3fbda","tid":947084,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:13:45.000Z","msg":"都係貴<br />\n果頭真係好多鴨仔團<br />\n試過過馬路冇啦啦俾幾十個大陸人包圍<br />\n好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021d1179ba3d1dcca4edce4dca876171b686bcc0","tid":947084,"uid":105856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"樓下幾十部旅遊巴<br />\n而家個巴士站隔離仲劃埋泊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12182d1c536dce26216f8083daa288bfc6262b4d","tid":947084,"uid